reviewText: I already had this tape, but can always use an extra

I am not enjoying this at all.  I was looking for Chet Atkins doing a duet with a female singer, doing the song "Vincent".  What I
got is a very poor recording!

Loved this!  So many country stars, so much good music and many laughs.  Well worth the purchase. I would recommend this to those who grew up listening to Bobby Bare, Johnny Paycheck, Charlie Walker, Johnny Russell, Crystal Gale, Lorri Morgan, etc.
This is a video which will be transferred to dvd and i am sure that my friend whom it ordered it for is going to love it
product seems satisfactory. I really don't need any more words to describe my reaction to the product, but it seems that you do.
SO GOOD TO SEE OLD COUNTRY STARS-ESPECIALLY THOSE WHO ARE GONE.  BROUGHT BACK GOOD MEMORIES. WOULD LIKE TO SEE MORE OF THESE.
We loved this video.  We are big country music fans We invited friends over and it was enjoyed by one and all.
